Novak Djokovic Evens U.S. Open Semifinal With Federer at Two Sets Apiece

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-09-10T20:18:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-10/novak-djokovic-evens-u-s-open-semifinal-with-federer-at-two-sets-apiece.html
Top seed Novak Djokovic has won the
last two sets to even his U.S. Open semifinal against five-time
champion  Roger Federer  at two sets apiece, forcing the match
into a decisive fifth set.   Federer, of  Switzerland , won 7-6 (9-7) in the first set
against Djokovic, from  Serbia . Federer won the second set 6-4.  Djokovic won the third set 6-3 and the fourth set 6-2.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  